				 class="stand-first-alone"												                data-component="comp : r2 : Gallery : standfirst_cta"
			>The newly refurbished V&amp;A fashion galleries play host to a dazzling array of ballgowns, dinner dresses, eyecatching red carpet robes and catwalk sensations in celebration of British glamour since the 1950s</p>
		
		
